display_long_description:
# It Has Awakened.

A new catastrophe rises in the zombie world: the giant mecha BUST.
Pilot a powerful mecha suit and tear through the massive battlefield.
Upgrade your machine and make this apocalypse your stage.
[media]

# A New Battlefield Opens.

A brand-new adventure across vast deserts and unknown spacecraft.
Grotesque zombies lurk across the map.
Stay alert. Bigger, deadlier battles begin now.
[media]

# Not All Zombies Are the Same.

Some rush straight at you, some fly above you, others sneak up on you… 
And who knows? Even stranger and scarier zombies are waiting ahead.
[media]

# The More Weapons, the Better.

From grenade launchers to hookshots and boosters, your power keeps evolving.
Master them all and rise as the strongest chicken alive.
[media]

# More Kills. Bigger Rewards.

Take down more zombies to stack bigger rewards.
Scores, coins, feathers, and more follow every victory.
Defeat more zombies, even your friends.
[media]

# Style Still Matters.

In the apocalypse, your look can be legendary or wildly ridiculous. 
Rock dripped-out fits and show off your unique style with other players!
[media]

# More Fun News and Events on Discord!

Join our Discord for the latest updates, events, and community fun.

👉 discord.gg/chickingdead
